OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F345A1781628468
OL,3,CTwo people fight for life in hospital
OL,4,Cafter early hours shooting
OL,6,FPolice are investigating after two
OL,7,Fpeople, including a teenage boy, were
OL,8,Fshot in the early hours of this
OL,9,Fmorning.
OL,11,FWest Midlands Police blocked off
OL,12,FVauxhall Crescent, near the junction
OL,13,Fwith Rover Drive, in Castle Bromwich,
OL,14,Fat around 2:40 am on Monday.
OL,16,FA man and a teenage boy have been
OL,17,Ftaken to the hospital with life-
OL,18,Fthreatening injuries. Police say the
OL,19,Finvestigation is still in its early
OL,20,Fstages, but no one has been arrested
OL,21,Fyet.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G1/5
