OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F345A1781628468
OL,3,CTwo people fight for life in hospital
OL,4,Cafter early hours shooting
OL,6,FIn a statement, police said: "We are
OL,7,Finvestigating after shots were fired
OL,8,Fin Vauxhall Crescent, Smith's Wood,
OL,9,Fthis morning.
OL,11,F"We were called after a man and a
OL,12,Fteenage boy were injured just before
OL,13,F2.40 am today (15 June).
OL,15,F"They were taken to hospital with
OL,16,Fgunshot wounds with their injuries
OL,17,Finitially believed to be life-
OL,18,Fthreatening.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G2/5
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,346,340,120,260,000,100
PN,34503
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F345A1781628468
OL,3,CTwo people fight for life in hospital
OL,4,Cafter early hours shooting
OL,6,F"Our investigation is in its early
OL,7,Fstages. We will have officers in the
OL,8,Farea carrying out reassurance patrols.
OL,10,F"Anyone with information, or who may
OL,11,Fhave been in the area at the time to
OL,12,Fget in contact on 101 or via the Live
OL,13,FChat option on our website quoting
OL,14,Fincident number 313 of 15 June.
OL,16,F"We have also set up our Major
OL,17,FIncident Public Portal (MIPP) where
OL,18,Fany still or moving images can be
OL,19,Fsubmitted directly."
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G3/5
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
