PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F345A1781628468
OL,3,CTwo people fight for life in hospital
OL,4,Cafter early hours shooting
OL,6,FAn ambulance spokeswoman said: "We
OL,7,Fwere called to Vauxhall Crescent,
OL,8,FCastle Bromwich, at 2.35 am this
OL,9,Fmorning.
OL,11,F"Two paramedic officers, two
OL,12,Fambulances, a MERIT trauma team, HART
OL,13,Fparamedics and a Critical Care car
OL,14,Ffrom The Air Ambulance Service
OL,15,Fresponded to the incident. Two people
OL,16,Freceived trauma care for serious
OL,17,Finjuries.
OL,19,F"They were conveyed on blue lights and
OL,20,Fsirens to hospital for further
OL,21,Fspecialist care."
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G4/5
